  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p784329/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201602/1a295c8c5b7447debc9e7fa7cb4a03cf.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《BBC英音模仿秀》是沪江社团的原创口语社刊，主持人对音频进行重点讲解和示范模仿，并对大家递交的口语模仿作品进行一对一的点评哦！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>今日主持人：<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">苏殷歉</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>10秒音频： </strong><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p784329\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>模仿文本：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t\tMy name is Tom Clarkson, and I'm joined to go through today's event by Jack Nicholls, who was calling the race from the ComBox, and Mark Gallagher, our chief analyst. That was breathless, Jack. Have you got your breath back?我是汤姆&middot;克拉森。即将跟我一起回顾赛事的是杰克&middot;尼科尔斯，他刚刚在演播室进行赛事解说，以及我们的首席分析师马克&middot;盖拉格。这场比赛真是紧张得让人喘不过气来。杰克，呼吸调整好了没？</div>\n\t<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t\t<strong>语调示意图：</strong></p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t<img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201605/a88560ba-2c6f-4052-a265-e48edc4389d3.png\" style=\"line-height: 28px; width: 500px; font-family: 'helvetica neue', 'hiragino sans gb', 'microsoft yahei', 'wenquanyi micro hei', sans-serif; height: 212px; font-size: 16px;\" /></p>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<strong>重点单词发音讲解：</strong><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\tClarkson /ˈklɑːksən/ 汤姆&middot;克拉森<br />\n\tJack Nicholls　杰克&middot;尼科尔斯<br />\n\tMark Gallagher 马克&middot;盖拉格</p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167839822843/\" target=\"_blank\">快来模仿秀现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;&nbsp;</a><span style=\"line-height: 25px;\">可以得到主持人专业的点评哦！</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p784329/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" st